            <p props="electron">This callback reports the statistics of the video stream sent by the local device and is triggered every 2 seconds.</p>
            <p props="rn">This callback describes statistics of the video stream sent by the local device. It is triggered every 2 seconds.</p>
            <p props="flutter">This callback provides statistics about the local device's video stream every 2 seconds.</p>
            <p props="unity">This callback reports statistics about the local device sending video streams. It is triggered every 2 seconds.</p>
